title: The Other Side Of The Door (Taylor's Version)
description:
The other side of the door is the other side of the fairytale.. but we get into all of that!
What does this song mean? And is it the response to one of her earlier songs?
Nick, Amy, Lacey and Ana discuss and dissect!
What did we miss? What else should we cover? Please let us know!
